Uses of Package
courses

Packages that use courses
courses   
io   
users   
 

Classes in courses used by courses
Course
          Contains information about a course like course title, level, number of credit hours, etc., but not information about a specific section like who teaches it.
Day
          Provides the days of the week individually or as a list of all days.
DaySlot
          DaySlot is a combination of days on which a Section may be offered.
GeneralTime
          A general division of the day.
Schedule
          Represents a Schedule.
Section
          Sections represent actual course offerings.
Time
          The time of day on a 24 hour clock.
TimeSlot
          Represents a combination of Days and a duration of time when a Section can meet.
